item.description: A show of support and a convoy to Manchester ( 1 of 3) arrives at around 2pm. Go to and read up on what has happened to this man. This is very important so please attend. There are multiple locations to meet. Rochester Commons 12:10pm leaves at 12:20 sharp. We will then move to pick up more at the Hannafords parking lot in Dover on Central Ave at 12:35 leaves at 12:45 sharp. Heading to the Portsmouth Traffic Circle (park at liquor store parking lot) at 12:55pm leaves at 1:05 sharp and heads to Manchester. This is an important rally please attend and show how the Live Free or Die state defends a man's liberty. This is a showing to the rest of our nation how determined we are to stand up for right and defend liberty. Come!!!! Bring your flags and yellow and black are the colors to wear or show if possible. Semper Fi, Jerry
